tisfaction%20and%20happiness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%2C%20I%20think%20it%20was%20very%20important%20for%20me%20to%20do%20something%20and%20bring%20the%20team%20in%20a%20position%20where%20there%20is%20a%20little%20comfort%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20batting%20order%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20to%20reach%20this%20point%2C%20India%20had%20to%20wade%20through%20a%20sea%20of%20criticism%2C%20particularly%20after%20the%20management's%20decision%20to%20pick%20five%20spinners%20%E2%80%94%20Ravindra%20Jadeja%2C%20Axar%20Patel%2C%20Kuldeep%20Yadav%2C%20Varun%20Chakravarthy%20and%20Washington%20Sundar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20four%20played%20and%20contributed%20consistently%20in%20India's%20victories%20%E2%80%94%20either%20by%20taking%20wickets%20or%20choking%20the%20run%20flow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20thought%20leaders%20were%20never%20in%20doubt%20of%20their%20strategy%2C%20and%20close%20observations%20of%20the%20earlier%20matches%20in%20Dubai%20such%20as%20ILT20%20helped%20them%20arrive%20at%20that%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20knew%20the%20conditions%20would%20be%20difficult%2C%20but%20we%20adapted%20well.%20We%20had%20to%20go%20with%20more%20spinners%20than%20the%20seamers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStaying%20in%20Dubai%20for%20the%20ICC%20showpiece%20was%20a%20decision%20beyond%20their%20control%2C%20for%20which%20the%20team%20came%20under%20fire%20for%20no%20real%20reason.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnmindful%20of%20such%20outside%20talks%2C%20Rohit%20said%20India%20were%20smart%20enough%20to%20use%20the%20conditions%20to%20their%20advantage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20saw%20how%20much%20these%20surfaces%20were%20used%20before%20we%20came%20here.%20I%20knew%20that%20the%20slower%20bowlers%20will%20come%20into%20play.%20So%2C%20we%20wanted%20to%20pick%20the%20squad%20based%20on%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20selecting%20the%20right%20squad%20is%20different%20from%20actually%20winning%20the%20matches%20because%2C%20as%20Gambhir%20hinted%20earlier%2C%20the%20four%20pitches%20used%20at%20the%20DICS%20offered%20different%20challenges%20to%20the%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKeeping%20the%20teams%20under%20240s%20under%20250%20is%20a%20big%20effort.%20We%20think%20that%20the%20wicket%20is%20helping%20the%20spinners.%20But%20you%20must%20have%20seen%20that%20in%20a%20few%20matches%2C%20no%20ball%20has%20turned%20in%20such%20a%20way%20that%20the%20ball%20is%20turning%20every%20time%2C%20in%20every%20over%2C%26quot%3B%20Rohit%20acknowledged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20bowlers%20might%20have%20had%20a%20certain%20edge%20because%20of%20that%20unpredictable%20spin%2C%20it%20put%20the%20batters%20under%20greater%20peril.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSometimes%2C%20one%20or%20two%20balls%20turn%20in%20between%2C%20but%20that%20is%20the%20challenge%20that%20you%20are%20facing%20as%20a%20batter.%20You%20don't%20have%20to%20be%20ready%20for%20the%20ball%20that%20is%20turning.%20But%20it's%20the%20straight%20ball.%E2%80%9D%20Kohli's%20dismissal%20in%20the%20final%20underlined%20that%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20master%20batter%2C%20who%20has%20made%20218%20runs%20at%20an%20average%20of%2054%20with%20a%20hundred%20and%20a%20fifty%20to%20quell%20the%20talks%20around%20his%20form%2C%20played%20for%20the%20turn%20but%20off-spinner%20Michael%20Bracewell's%20stock%20ball%20was%20straighter%20than%20he%20expected%20to%20get%20caught%20in%20front%20of%20the%20wicket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20straight%20ball%20that%20is%20coming%2C%20which%20is%2080%25%20out%20of%20100%2C%20or%2070%25%2C%20you%20have%20to%20be%20ready%20for%20that.%20So%2C%20I%20think%20that%20is%20the%20adaptation%20and%20that%20is%20what%20these%20guys%20have%20shown%20in%20the%20middle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20proud%20of%20them%20because%20India%20is%20a%20bloody%20good%20team%20without%20a%20doubt%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2