tGPT.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia's%20trailing%2012-month%20price-to-earnings%20ratio%20dropped%20to%2036.4%20times%20on%20Monday%2C%20according%20to%20data%20from%20YCharts.%20The%20decline%20has%20been%20driven%20by%20a%20sharp%20price%20decline%20in%20Nvidia's%20stock%2C%20which%20finished%20Monday%20down%2030%25%20from%20its%20intraday%20record%20high%20reached%20in%20early%20January.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20valuation%20multiple%20decline%20makes%20Nvidia%20cheaper%20today%20than%20it%20was%20when%20ChatGPT%20was%20first%20released%20on%20November%2030%2C%202022.%20The%20stock%20is%20trading%20at%20its%20cheapest%20level%20since%20August%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBen%20Reitzes%2C%20managing%20director%20at%20Melius%20Research%2C%20said%20the%20valuation%20dynamic%20for%20Nvidia%20also%20holds%20true%20on%20a%20forward%20P%2FE%20ratio%2C%20which%20incorporates%20Wall%20Street's%20year-ahead%20earnings%20estimates%20for%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Reitzes%2C%20with%20a%20forward%20P%2FE%20ratio%20of%2024%20times%2C%20Nvidia%20stock%20is%2041%25%20cheaper%20than%20it%20was%20when%20ChatGPT%20launched.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22896%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22nvidia%20valuations%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67cf38fc585f1dff88b1affb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22522%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EMelius%20Research%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20an%20impressive%20feat%20given%20that%20Nvidia%20shares%20have%20soared%20583%25%20since%20OpenAI%20released%20ChatGPT%20to%20the%20masses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20case%2C%20the%20stock-price%20surge%20was%20backed%20up%20by%20profits%2C%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENvidia's%20GPU%20business%20boomed%3C%2Fa%3E%20due%20to%20strong%20demand%20from%20AI%20companies.%20Nvidia's%20net%20income%20in%20the%20fiscal%20year%202025%20soared%20788%25