om%20current%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-stock-price-correction-plunges-valuation-metric-levels-before-chatgpt-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741638730000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6747863e9f2901eb60377685%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-stock-price-correction-plunges-valuation-metric-levels-before-chatgpt-2025-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nvidia's%20trailing%2012-month%20P%2FE%20ratio%20dropped%20on%20Monday%20to%20its%20lowest%20level%20since%20August%202019.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mfox%40businessinsider.com%20(Matthew%20Fox)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A77%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-stock-price-correction-plunges-valuation-metric-levels-before-chatgpt-2025-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22YouTube%E2%80%99s%20Biggest%20Stars%20Talk%20Podcasting%2C%20Advise%20for%20Future%20Creators%20and%20Wanting%20Emmy%20Recognition%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741638632000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236333539%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20special%20live%20taping%20of%20Variety%E2%80%99s%20Awards%20Circuit%20Podcast%20at%20SXSW%2C%20some%20of%20YouTube%E2%80%99s%20most%20influential%20creators%20sat%20down%20to%20discuss%20the%20platform%E2%80%99s%20evolution%20as%20it%20approaches%20its%2020th%20anniversary%20this%20April.%20Joining%20the%20conversation%20were%20Sean%20Evans%2C%20Host%20of%20%E2%80%9CHot%20Ones%E2%80%9D%20and%20Chief%20Creative%20Officer%2C%20First%20We%20Feast%3B%20Rhett%20McLaughlin%20and%20Link%20Neal%2C%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Clayton%20Davis%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7