li%3E%3Cli%3EThis%20article%20is%20part%20of%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Fai-in-action%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20in%20Action%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20series%20exploring%20how%20companies%20are%20implementing%20AI%20innovations.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EJohnson%20%26amp%3B%20Johnson%20is%20embracing%20the%20concept%20of%20a%20bilingual%20employee%20%E2%80%94%20but%20not%20in%20the%20classic%20sense.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20pharmaceutical%20company%2C%20literacy%20is%20needed%20in%20specialized%20and%20core%20job%20skills%2C%20including%20research%2C%20supply%20chain%2C%20and%20finance.%20Then%20there's%20fluency%20in%20AI%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20so%20many%20ways%20we've%20been%20using%20AI%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jim%20Swanson%2C%20the%20chief%20information%20officer%20of%20J%26amp%3BJ.%20%26quot%3BBut%20to%20do%20that%20effectively%2C%20we%20had%20to%20really%20create%20a%20curriculum%20and%20a%20mindset%20around%20upskilling.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20than%2056%2C000%20of%20J%26amp%3BJ's%20138%2C000%20workers%20have%20taken%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgenerative-ai-evolution-software-companies-develop-ai-agents-workforce-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egenerative%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20training%20course%2C%20which%20is%20required%20before%20any%20employee%20is%20authorized%20to%20use%20the%20technology.%20After%20training%2C%20J%26amp%3BJ's%20employees%20can%20utilize%20generative%20AI%20tools%20for%20summarization%20and%20prompt%20engineering%2C%20the%20latter%20a%20skill%20to%20ask%20the%20right%20question%20to%20get%20the%20best%20output%20from%20a%20large%20language%20model.%20A%20separate%2C%20more%20in-depth%20digital%20boot%20camp%20that%20covers%20topics%20including%20AI%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fwhat-is-augmented-reality%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaugmented%20reality%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20automation%20has%20recorded%20more%20than%2037%2C000%20cumulative%20hours%20of%20training%20from%20more%20than%2014%2C000%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGenerative%20AI%20offers%20the%20promise%20of%20more%20quickly%20identifying%20compounds%20for%20new%20treatments%20and%20vaccines%2C%20accelerating%20drug%20development%2C%20streamlining%20regulatory%20compliance%2C%20optimizing%20which%20patients%20are%20best%20suited%20for%20clinical%20trials%2C%20and%20improving%20how%20new%20drugs%20are%20marketed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDeborah%20Golden%2C%20Deloitte's%20US%20chief%20innovation%20officer%2C%20said%20these%20advancements%20were%20poised%20to%20change%20which%20skills%20the%20pharmaceutical%20industry%20prioritizes%20in%20recruitment.%20Biology%20and%20chemistry%20knowledge%20will%20still%20be%20needed%2C%20but%20it%20isn't%20as%20essential%20for%20newer%20roles%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsalesforce-ai-executive-agency-problem-solving-more-important-learning-code-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20engineers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20other%20new%20roles%20might%20require%20a%20mix%20of%20traditional%20expertise%20and%20AI%20know-how%20if%20AI-driven%20drug%20discovery%20proliferates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20think%20about%20how%20AI%20is%20shifting%20the%20balance%20and%20the%20talent%20requirements%2C%20you%20really%20need%20to%20be%20able%20to%20speak%20both%20the%20language%20of%20biology%20and%20AI%20models%2C%26quot%3B%20Golden%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cec3cb5a-0731-4fe1-b746-79236b712a1f%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20AI%20is%20changing%20drug%20development%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGenerative%20AI%20could%20save%20the%20pharmaceutical%20industry%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mckinsey.com%2Findustries%2Flife-sciences%2Four-insights%2Fgenerative-ai-in-the-pharmaceutical-industry-moving-from-hype-to-reality%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20tens%20of%20billions%20of%20dollars%20each%20year%3C%2Fa%3E%20through%20improved%20productivity%20within%20drug%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJ%26amp%3BJ%2C%20the%20maker%20of%20treatments%20like%20the%20immunosuppressive%20drug%20Stelara%20and%20Darzalex%2C%20a%20medication%20for%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Etreating%20the%20cancer%20multiple%20myeloma%2C%20has%20used%20more%20traditional%20forms%20of%20AI%20for%20almost%20a%20decade.%20Use%20cases%20include%20AI-enabled%20software%20tools%20that%20can%20guide%20a%20surgeon%20through%20a%20procedure%2C%20speed%20up%20drug%20discovery%2C%20and%20help%20drug%20makers%20manage%20inventory%20more%20effectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20J%26amp%3BJ%20piloted%20a%20six-week%20digital%20immersion%20program%20that%20focused%20on%20AI%2C%20data%20science%2C%20and%20other%20emerging%20technologies.%20More%20than%202%2C500%20employees%20participated%20last%20year%2C%20taking%2090-minute%20classes%20each%20week%2C%20and%20J%26amp%3BJ%20is%20planning%20further%20expansion%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESwanson%20told%20Business%20Insider%20it%20was%20critical%20for%20company%20leaders%20to%20create%20a%20culture%20that%20promotes%20technological%20literacy.%20%26quot%3BWe've%20been%20around%20135%20years.%20We've%20had%20to%20reinvent%20ourselves%20multiple%20times%20to%20stay%20relevant%20and%20current%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pharmaceutical%20giant%20Merck's%20early%20generative%20AI%20investments%20included%20the%20development%20of%20a%20proprietary%20platform%20called%20GPTeal.%20Merck%20%E2%80%94%20which%20is%20responsible%20for%20the%20HPV%20vaccine%20Gardasil%20and%20the%20immunotherapy%20drug%20Keytruda%20%E2%80%94%20said%20that%20GPTeal%20gives%20employees%20access%20to%20large%20language%20models%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feverything-you-need-to-know-about-chat-gpt-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOpenAI's%20ChatGPT%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Meta's%20Llama%2C%20and%20Anthropic's%20Claude%20while%20keeping%20company%20data%20secure%20from%20external%20exposures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEmployees%20are%20also%20using%20generative%20AI%20to%20draft%20emails%20and%20memos%20and%20for%20other%20productivity-focused%20tasks%2C%20but%20Merck's%20aspirations%20are%20also%20getting%20bolder.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%2C%20the%20journey%20is%20clearly%20to%20identify%2C%20implement%2C%20track%2C%20and%20measure%20use%20cases%20that%20have%20a%20dramatic%20impact%20on%20our%20business%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ron%20Kim%2C%20a%20senior%20vice%20president%20and%20the%20chief%20technology%20officer%20of%20Merck.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGenerative%20AI%20allows%20Merck's%20employees%20more%20time%20to%20focus%20on%20higher-impact%20tasks.%20In%20drug%20discovery%2C%20for%20example%2C%20generative%20AI%20can%20help%20draft%20(human-reviewed)%20regulatory%20documents%20that%20are%20submitted%20to%20health%20authorities.%20%26quot%3BWe%20felt%20like%20some%20of%20our%20scientists%20were%20taking%20time%20being%20copyeditors%2C%26quot%3B%20Kim%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20not%20what%20they%20trained%20for.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKim%20said%20more%20than%2050%2C000%20Merck%20employees%20were%20using%20GPTeal%20regularly.%20The%20company%20supported%20upskilling%20through%20a%20mix%20of%20self-serve%20digital%20training%20courses%2C%20monthly%20webcasts%20focused%20on%20generative%20AI%2C%20and%20boot%20camps%20for%20software%20developers%20that%20could%20last%20anywhere%20from%20half%20a%20day%20to%2010%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a2f33f1c-1cb9-453d-90c1-6bdff60dff44%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAI%20can%20appeal%20to%20pharmaceutical%20companies%20of%20various%20sizes%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDr.%20Daniel%20Stevens%2C%20the%20chief%20medical%20officer%20at%20Blue%20Earth%20Therapeutics%2C%20said%20AI%20was%20alluring%20to%20the%20clinical-stage%20radiopharmaceutical%20company%20because%2C%20as%20a%20small%20startup%20founded%20in%202021%2C%20it%20has%20to%20be%20judicious%20with%20how%20it%20spends%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20application%20of%20artificial%20intelligence%20is%20of%20interest%2C%20because%20it%20may%20help%20us%20with%20some%20of%20our%20efficiency%20goals%2C%26quot%3B%20Stevens%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20%2476.5%20million%20Series%20A%20in%20October%2C%20which%20included%20funding%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-tech-innovations-help-medical-billing-diagnostics-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehealthcare%3C%2Fa%3E%20investment%20firm%20Soleus%20Capital%20and%20the%20diagnostic%20imaging%20company%20Bracco%20Diagnostics%2C%20was%20mostly%20intended%20to%20support%20clinical%20trials%20that%20will%20assess%20the%20safety%20and%20effectiveness%20of%20new%20prostate%20cancer%20treatments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStevens%20said%20that%20with%20just%2020%20full-time%20employees%2C%20Blue%20Earth%20has%20not%20yet%20needed%20to%20offer%20AI%20upskill%20training.%20He%20added%20that%20when%20Blue%20Earth%20grows%20its%20employee%20base%20and%20is%20ready%20to%20offer%20instruction%20about%20the%20technology%2C%20it%20plans%20to%20use%20online%20courses%20and%20AI%20certifications%20from%20external%20vendors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEli%20Lilly%2C%20the%20pharmaceutical%20giant%20behind%20treatments%20including%20the%20antidepressant%20Prozac%20and%20the%20type%202%20diabetes%20and%20weight%20loss%20medicine%20Mounjaro%2C%20has%20used%20generative%20AI%20to%20support%20the%20research%20of%20both%20small%20and%20large%20molecules.%20The%20company%20also%20used%20AI%20to%20generate%20documentation%20for%20clinical%20trials%20and%20create%20materials%20for%20regulatory%20submissions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20ChatGPT%20launched%2C%20major%20employers%20such%20as%20Apple%20and%20Amazon%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchatgpt-companies-issued-bans-restrictions-openai-ai-amazon-apple-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erestricted%20employee%20use%20of%20the%20popular%20chatbot%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20many%20citing%20concerns%20about%20data%20privacy.%20%26quot%3BWe%20went%20in%20the%20exact%20opposite%20direction%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Diogo%20Rau%2C%20the%20chief%20information%20and%20digital%20officer%20at%20Eli%20Lilly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERau%20encouraged%20Eli%20Lilly's%20workforce%20to%20embrace%20the%20tool%20without%20exposing%20sensitive%20company%20information%2C%20similar%20to%20how%20an%20employee%20might%20use%20Google%20Search.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20told%20everybody%20you%20need%20to%20use%20it%2C%20you%20need%20to%20start%20bringing%20ChatGPT%20into%20your%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Rau.%20But%2C%20he%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BDon't%20put%20anything%20in%20there%20that%20you%20don't%20want%20to%20get%20out.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20also%20internally%20sought%20to%20bolster%20interest%20with%20an%20%26quot%3BAI%20Games%26quot%3B%20competition%20timed%20to%20the%20Summer%20Olympics%20in%20Paris.%20Contests%20involved%20using%20a%20chatbot%20to%20write%20a%20message%20to%20a%20colleague%20or%20relying%20on%20generative%20AI%20to%20make%20a%20quiz%20about%20Eli%20Lilly's%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202024%2C%20Eli%20Lilly%20also%20encouraged%20all%20employees%20and%20managers%20to%20use%20generative%20AI%20for%20their%20year-end%20reviews.%20This%20year%2C%20the%20company%20is%20set%20to%20require%20all%20senior%20leaders%20and%20managers%20to%20obtain%20an%20AI%20certification.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20got%20a%20workforce%20that%20is%20embracing%20AI%2C%26quot%3B%20Rau%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20employees%20often%20stopped%20him%20in%20the%20office%20or%20emailed%20him%20to%20share%20the%20ways%20they%20were%20applying%20AI%20to%20their%20daily%20work%20tasks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default