t%20comfortable%2C%20then%20wrap%20the%20scarf%20around%20your%20neck.%20Velcro%20on%20the%20other%20end%20of%20the%20ribs%20holds%20the%20wrap%20in%20place%20while%20you%20doze%20off.%20The%20ribs%20have%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20flexibility%20to%20eliminate%20any%20pressure%20points%20or%20discomfort.%20%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%94%20David%20Slotnick%2C%20contributor%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EA%20light%20that%20slowly%20dims%20at%20night%20and%20brightens%20in%20the%20morning%20to%20mimic%20a%20sunrise%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20casper%20glow%20light%20sits%20on%20a%20night%20table%20near%20a%20book%20and%20pair%20of%20glasses.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5e5574e9fee23d3f174b0175%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Casper%20Glow%20Light%20helps%20you%20unwind%20at%20night%20and%20get%20going%20in%20the%20morning%20using%20light.%3Cp%3ECasper%2FInstagram%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECasper%20Glow%20Light%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20circadian%20rhythm%20is%20hyperactive%2C%20which%20means%20my%20sleep%20is%20easily%20disrupted%20by%20late-night%20screen%20time%20and%20bright%20lighting%20before%20bed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Glow%20Light%20from%20Casper%20is%20the%20one%20tool%20I've%20found%20that%20consistently%20puts%20me%20to%20sleep.%20It%20starts%20out%20bright%20enough%20to%20read%20a%20book%20but%20dims%20down%20over%20the%20course%20of%20about%2045%20minutes%20until%20it's%20off.%20(You%20can%20adjust%20the%20schedule%20using%20an%20app%2C%20though%20I've%20never%20tried%20it).%20Because%20it%20mimics%20the%20setting%20sun%2C%20my%20body%20responds%20well%20and%20knows%20it's%20time%20to%20sleep%20by%20about%2020%20minutes%20into%20the%20light's%20cycle.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20turn%20the%20light%20on%20or%20off%2C%20you%20just%20flip%20it%20over%3B%20you%20can%20also%20twist%20it%20left%20and%20right%20to%20bring%20the%20brightness%20up%20or%20down%20and%20shake%20it%20while%20it's%20off%20to%20turn%20it%20into%20a%20night%20light.%20%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%94%20Stephanie%20Hallett%2C%20former%20senior%20editor%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERead%20our%20full%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fcasper-glow-light-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECasper%20Glow%20Light%20review%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Ffavorite-sleep-products%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741633201000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67cf2f94b8b41a9673fa30b1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Ffavorite-sleep-products%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22We%20asked%20the%20Business%20Insider%20Reviews%20team%20for%20the%20sleep%20products%20they%20swear%20by%20for%20better%20sleep%2C%20from%20weighted%20blankets%20to%20cooling%20essentials.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jbrains%40businessinsider.com%20(James%20Brains%2CKinsley%20Searles)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Ffavorite-sleep-products%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22People%20are%20listing%20invite%20codes%20to%20Chinese%20AI%20agent%20Manus%20for%20%241%2C000%20and%20more%20on%20resale%20sites%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20hand%20in%20shadow%20holds%20up%20a%20phone%20with%20the%20%26quot%3BManus%26quot%3B%20logo%20on%20screen%2C%20written%20in%20all%20lowercase%20black%20text%2C%20with%20a%20stylized%20hand%20snapping%20next%20to%20it.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67cf1c0969253ccddf98c5c0%3Fformat%3D