y%20for%20US%20brands%20to%20expand%20into%20a%20fast-growing%20market%20%E2%80%94%20and%20hedge%20against%20a%20possible%20TikTok%20ban.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeauty%20brand%20KimChi%20Chic%20Beauty%2C%20supplement%20brand%20Beast%20Bites%2C%20and%20security-camera%20brand%20Wyze%20are%20among%20the%20US%20companies%20planning%20to%20expand%20into%20Mexico%2C%20per%20two%20Shop%20agencies%20that%20work%20with%20the%20firms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20logical%20play%20for%20any%20seller%20that%20saw%20success%20or%20could%20see%20success%20on%20TikTok%20Shop%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20William%20August%2C%20CEO%20of%20the%20social-commerce%20agency%20Outlandish%2C%20which%20runs%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcreator-startup-outlandish-opens-new-hybrid-shopping-experience-in-la-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elivestream%20facility%20in%20Los%20Angeles%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20recently%20set%20up%20operations%20in%20Mexico.%20%26quot%3BRegardless%20of%20what%20happens%20in%20the%20US%2C%20they%20should%20be%20doing%20it%20anyway.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETikTok%20Shop%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-tiktok-shop-is-changing-e-commerce%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egrown%20quickly%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20US%20since%20it%20first%20began%20testing%20the%20feature%20there%20in%202022.%20But%20the%20app%20is%20operating%20on%20shaky%20ground%20due%20to%20a%20divestment%20law%20that%20requires%20its%20Chinese%20owner%2C%20ByteDance%2C%20to%20sell%20the%20app%20or%20essentially%20stop%20operating%20in%20the%20US.%20%3Cspan%3EWhile%20%3C%2Fspan%3Ethat%20hasn't%20deterred%20%3Cspan%3Emany%20brands%20%3C%2Fspan%3Ethat%3Cspan%3E%20sell%20goods%20on%20TikTok%20in%20the%20US%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20some%20are%20busy%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-sellers-brace-for-doomsday-as-us-ban-approaches-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ediversifying%3C%2Fa%3E