%3B%20and%20the%20Diversity%2C%20Equity%2C%20Inclusion%2C%20and%20Accessibility%20branch%20of%20the%20Office%20of%20Diversity%20and%20Equal%20Opportunity.%20An%20agency%20spokesperson%20told%20BI%20that%2023%20individuals%20were%20fired.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNASA's%20Office%20of%20the%20Chief%20Scientist%20is%20tasked%20with%20ensuring%20that%20all%20the%20Agency's%20scientific%20endeavors%20align%20with%20the%20Administration's%20goals.%20Eliminating%20the%20office%20sends%20a%20chilling%20message%20that%20NASA's%20scientists%20aren't%20part%20of%20the%20nation's%20goals%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20current%20NASA%20employee%20told%20BI%20in%20a%20written%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPetro%20said%20the%20changes%20put%20the%20agency%20in%20compliance%20with%20President%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDonald%20Trump's%3C%2Fa%3E%20executive%20order%20to%20implement%20the%20White%20House%20DOGE%20office's%20workplace%20restructuring.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20wrote%20that%20Monday%20marked%20the%20beginning%20of%20NASA's%20reduction%20in%20force%20effort.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20this%20will%20mean%20making%20difficult%20adjustments%2C%20we're%20viewing%20this%20as%20an%20opportunity%20to%20reshape%20our%20workforce%2C%20ensuring%20we%20are%20doing%20what%20is%20statutorily%20required%20of%20us%2C%20while%20also%20providing%20American%20citizens%20with%20an%20efficient%20and%20effective%20agency%2C%26quot%3B%20Petro%20wrote%20in%20the%20email.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20clear%20if%20all%20employees%20in%20the%20departments%20were%20terminated%2C%20or%20if%20some%20might%20be%20moved%20to%20different%20areas%20within%20NASA.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20small%20number%20of%20individuals%20received%20notification%20Monday%20they%20are%20a%20part%20of%20NASA's%20RIF.%20If%20they're%20eligible%2C%20those%20employees%20may%20opt%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20Voluntary%20Early%20Retirement%20Authority%2C%20or%20VERA%2C%20or%20complete%20the%20RIF%20process%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20NASA%20spokesperson%20told%20BI%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20DOGE%20and%20the%20White%20House%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20restructuring%20plans%20from%20NASA%20follow%20weeks%20of%20changes%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffederal-agencies-musk-doge-targeted-list-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efederal%20workforce%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20Trump%20administration%20has%20fired%20thousands%20of%20workers%20across%20a%20range%20of%20federal%20agencies%20and%20has%20cut%20billions%20of%20dollars%20in%20federal%20spending%20programs.%20The%20Office%20of%20Personnel%20Management%20also%20instructed%20all%20federal%20agencies%20to%20develop%20reorganization%20plans%20by%20March%2013.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20a%20tip%3F%20Contact%20these%20reporters%20via%20Signal%20at%20asheffey.97%20or%20alicetecotzky.05%20or%20via%20email%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aasheffey%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Easheffey%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20or%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aatecotzky%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Eatecotzky%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%20Use%20a%20personal%20email%20address%20and%20a%20nonwork%20device%3B%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsider-guide-to-securely-sharing-whistleblower-information-about-powerful-institutions-2021-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ehere's%20our%20guide%20to%20sharing%20information%20securely%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnasa-reduction-in-force-plans-depa