wever%2C%20faced%20delays%2C%20space%20debris%20threats%2C%20helium%20leaks%20and%20technical%20glitches%20on%20the%20Starliner%20spacecraft%20on%20which%20they%20travelled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Williams%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20back%20on%20Earth%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnasa-astronauts-sunita-williams-butch-wilmore-set-to-return-on-this-date-7892431%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enext%20few%20weeks%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20what%20is%20it%20that%20Ms%20Williams%20is%20doing%20while%20orbiting%20the%20Earth%2C%20nearly%20400%20kilometres%20above%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20way%20up%20to%20the%20ISS%2C%20the%20astronaut%20piloted%20the%20Boeing%20Starliner%20she%20helped%20develop%2C%20and%20which%20cost%20NASA%204.2%20billion%20dollars.%20She%2C%20along%20with%20Mr%20Wilmore%2C%20saw%20the%20Starliner%20depart%20from%20the%20ISS%20and%20land%20safely%20on%20Earth%20on%20September%207.%20She%20also%20became%20the%20first%20woman%20astronaut%20to%20test%20a%20space%20capsule.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20ISS%2C%20Ms%20Williams%20helped%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20maintenance%20and%20cleaning%20of%20the%20football%20field-sized%20space%20station.%20She%20and%20her%20colleague%20helped%20replace%20many%20old%20instruments%20on%20the%20ISS%20and%20send%20back%20a%20lot%20of%20trash%20to%20Earth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20NASA%2C%20Ms%20Williams%2C%20Mr%20Wilmore%20and%20another%20astronaut%2C%20Nick%20Hague%2C%20%26quot%3Bcompleted%20more%20than%20900%20hours%20of%20research%20between%20over%20150%20unique%20scientific%20experiments%20and%20technology%20demonstrations%20during%20their%20stay%20aboard%20the%20orbiting%20laboratory%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Ms%20William's%20stay%20got%20extended%20from%20weeks%20to%20months%2C%20the%20veteran%20of%20the%20three-space%20flight%20was%20then%20promoted%20to%20the%20role%20of%20ISS%20Commander%2C%20a%20rare%20distinction%20that%20placed%20the%20safety%20and%20security%20of%20the%20ISS%20on%20her%20shoulders.%20The%20ISS%20is%20possibly%20the%20single-most%20expensive%20engineering%20experiment%20ever%20to%20be%20undertaken%20by%20humans.%20It%20has%20continuously%20been%20inhabited%20by%20humans%20for%20the%20last%2025%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Williams%20had%20to%20accommodate%20extensive%20weight%20training%20in%20space%2C%20in%20her%20schedule%2C%20to%20keep%20her%20body%20fit%20and%20in%20shape%20as%20she%20floated%20around%20in%20near%20zero%20gravity%20in%20space.%20At%20%C2%A0one%20point%2C%20there%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmy-body-has-changed-but-sunita-williams-on-her-health-aboard-space-station-7012028%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eswirling%20%26quot%3Brumours%26quot%3B%20about%20her%20health%3C%2Fa%3E%20till%20she%20issued%20a%20clarification%2C%20saying%20she%20weighs%20the%20same%20as%20she%20did%20when%20she%20arrived%20at%20the%20ISS.%20Her%20%26quot%3Bwild%20hair%26quot%3B%20also%20garnered%20worldwide%20attention%2C%20with%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20saying%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20see%20the%20woman%20with%20the%20wild%20hair%2C%20good%2C%20solid%20head%20of%20hair%20she's%20got.%20There's%20no%20kidding%2C%20there's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdonald-trump-on-stranded-astronaut-sunita-williams-solid-head-of-hair-shes-got-7867049%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eno%20games%20with%20her%20hair%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20astronaut%20has%20also%20taken%20a%20long%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Findian-origin-sunita-williams-undertakes-spacewalk-after-12-years-7488241%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Espacewalk%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20also%20called%20an%20extra%20vehicular%20activity%20(EVA)%2C%20and%20has%20completed%2062%20hours%20and%20nine%20minutes%20on%20the%20activity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20her%20last%20space%20walk%20on%20January%2030%2C%20Ms%20Williams%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnasa-astronaut-sunita-williams-butch-wilmore-set-new-record-of-5-5-hour-spacewalk-7599914%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Espent%20five%20hours%20and%2026%20minutes%20on%20EVA%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20upgrade%20the%20ISS.%20A%20fortnight%20before%20that%2C%20on%20January%2016%2C%20she%20did%20a%20six-hour%20spacewalk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20has%20also%20done%20some%20tests%20and%20experiments%20on%20her%20own%20physiology%20to%20have%20a%20better%20understanding%20of%20how%20the%20body%20reacts%20to%20the%20space%20environment.%20On%20an%20earlier%20visit%2C%20she%20ran%20a%20marathon%20in%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20her%20outreach%20activities%2C%20Ms%20Williams%20sent%20Diwali%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdid-sunita-williams-take-santa-hats-on-6-day-iss-mission-nasa-responds-7328558%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChristmas%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20New%20Year%20greetings%20to%20humans%20on%20Earth%20and%20even%20held%20a%20session%20with%20students%20of%20a%20school%20named%20after%20her.%20She%20even%20wished%20the%20participants%20of%20the%202024%20Paris%20Olympics%20good%20luck%20from%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20other%20activities%2C%20the%20astronaut%20helped%20with%20some%20gardening%20in%20space%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwhy-nasas-sunita-williams-is-growing-lettuce-in-space-7169351%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewatering%20lettuce%20plants%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20studying%20them%2C%20in%20an%20effort%20which%2C%20according%20to%20NASA%2C%20could%20%26quot%3Bshow%20how%20less-than-ideal%20conditions%20affect%20plant%20growth%20and%20help%20scientists%20design%20systems%20to%20produce%20safe%20and%20nutritious%20food%20for%20crew%20members%20on%20future%20space%20journeys%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Williams%20also%20carried%20out%20experiments%20on%20how%20to%20recover%20water%20at%20the%20ISS%20through%20what%20NASA%20described%20as%20the%20packed%20bed%20reactors%2C%20referring%20to%20systems%20that%20%26quot%3Bpack%26quot%3B%20materials%20such%20as%20pellets%20or%20beads%20inside%20a%20structure%20to%20increase%20contact%20between%20any%20liquids%20and%20gasses%20flowing%20through%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20installed%20hardware%20for%20the%20Packed%20Bed%20Reactor%20Experiment%3A%20Water%20Recovery%20Series%20(PBRE-WRS)%20investigation%2C%20to%20examine%20how%20gravity%20affects%20these%20systems%20aboard%20the%20ISS.%20The%20results%20could%20help%20scientists%20design%20better%20reactors%20for%20water%20recovery%2C%20thermal%20management%2C%20fuel%20cells%20and%20other%20applications.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Mr%20Wilmore%20swabbed%20the%20exterior%20of%20the%20ISS%2C%20searching%20for%20life%20on%20the%20inside%20of%20the%20space%20station%2C%20his%20colleague%20experimented%20with%20other%20microbes.%20According%20to%20NASA%2C%20Ms%20Williams%20posed%20with%20bacteria%20and%20yeast%20samples%20for%20Rhodium%20Biomanufacturing%2003%2C%20part%20of%20an%20ongoing%20examination%20of%20microgravity's%20effects%20on%20bio-manufacturing%20engineered%20bacteria%20and%20yeast%20aboard%20the%20ISS.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENASA%20says%20microgravity%20causes%20changes%20in%20microbial%20cell%20growth%2C%20cell%20structure%20and%20metabolic%20activity%20that%20can%20affect%20bio-manufacturing%20processes.%20This%20investigation%20could%20explain%20the%20extent%20of%20these%20effects%20and%20advance%20the%20use%20of%20microbes%20to%20make%20food%2C%20pharmaceuticals%20and%20other%20products%20in%20space%2C%20reducing%20the%20cost%20of%20launching%20equipment%20and%20consumables%20from%20Earth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Williams%20also%20carried%20out%20the%20BioNutrients%20investigation%20that%20demonstrated%20technology%20to%20produce%20nutrients%20during%20long-duration%20space%20missions%20using%20engineered%20microbes%20like%20yeast.%20Food%20stored%20for%20long%20periods%20can%20lose%20vitamins%20and%20other%20nutrients%2C%20and%20this%20technology%20could%20provide%20a%20way%20to%20make%20supplements%20on%20demand.%20She%20prepared%20specially%20designed%20growth%20packets%20for%20the%20investigation%20aboard%20the%20ISS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20she%20returns%20to%20Earth%2C%20Ms%20Williams%20will%20make%20another%20record%20having%20flown%20four%20different%20space%20capsules%20-%20Space%20Shuttle%2C%20Soyuz%2C%20Boeing%20Starliner%20and%20SpaceX%20Crew%20Dragon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncidentally%2C%20during%20her%20long%20stay%20at%20the%20ISS%2C%20a%20seismic%20shift%20happened%20in%20the%20politics%20and%20governance%20in%20the%20US%2C%20and%20she%20became%20an%20unwarranted%20accomplice%20in%20the%20war%20between%20the%20Democrats%20and%20the%20Republicans.%20She%20did%20not%20wade%20into%20the%20war%20of%20words%2C%20steering%20clear%20and%20focusing%20on%20her%20singular%20job%20as%20an%20astronaut.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741629000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2F2ej5tah8_sunita-williams_625x300_10_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsunita-williams-news-return-spending-time-in-space-spacewalk-return-to-earth-international-space-station-7894324%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Indian-origin%20NASA%20astronaut%20Sunita%20Williams%20(Suni)%2C%20who%20has%20been%20dubbed%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bstranded%20astronaut%26quot%3B%20over%20his%20stay%20in%20space%20since%20June%20last%20year%2C%20has%20done%20some%20%26quot%3Bamazing%20experiments%26quot%3B%20and%20indulged%20in%20over%20900%20hours%20of%20research.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsunita-williams-news-return-spending-time-in-space-spacewalk-return-to-earth-international-space-station-7894324%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22ChatGPT%20using%20our%20content%20may%20lead%20to%20unfair%20competition%3A%20ANI%20to%20HC%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741628425000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fchatgpt-using-ani-content-to-train-its-model-will-dilute-our-mkt-ani-to-hc-125031001096_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Addressing%20the%20legal%20implications%20of%20public%20accessibility%2C%20Advocate%20Ramanujan%20argued%20that%20the%20mere%20availability%20of%20content%20in%20the%20public%20domain%20did%20not%20nullify%20copyright%20protections%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Devendra%20Fadnavis%20Backs%20Call%20To%20Remove%20Aurangzeb's%20Tomb%2C%20Slams%20Congress%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMaharashtra%20Chief%20Minister%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20today%20backed%20the%20call%20for%20the%20removal%20of%20the%20tomb%20of%20Mughal%20emperor%20Aurangzeb%20from%20Khulabad%20in%20Chhatrapati%20Sambhajinagar%20district.%20He%2C%20however%20said%20this%20has%20to%20be%20done%20through%20the%20law%2C%20since%20the%20previous%20Congress%20government%20had%20protected%20the%20tomb%20by%20handing%20it%20over%20to%20the%20Archaeological%20Society%20of%20India%20or%20ASI.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20all%20also%20want%20the%20same%20thing%2C%20but%20you%20need%20to%20do%20it%20within%20the%20framework%20of%20the%20law%2C%20because%20it%20is%20a%20protected%20site.%20The%20site%20was%20put%20under%20ASI's%20protection%20during%20the%20Congress%20regime%20some%20years%20back%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20the%20BJP's%20Satara%20MP%20Udayanraje%20Bhosale%2C%20a%20descendant%20of%20Maratha%20king%20Chhatrapati%20Shivaji%20Maharaj%2C%20had%20demanded%20that%20the%20tomb%20be%20razed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20is%20the%20need...%20send%20a%20JCB%20machine%20and%20raze%20his%20grave...%20he%20was%20a%20thief%20and%20lootera%20(robber)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThose%20who%20visit%20Aurangzeb's%20tomb%20and%20pay%20homage%20may%20be%20his%20future.%20They%20should%20take%20that%20tomb%20to%20their%20own%20homes%2C%20but%20the%20glorification%20of%20Aurangzeb%20will%20not%20be%20tolerated%20anymore%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BStrict%20action%26quot%3B%20should%20be%20taken%20against%20those%20who%20give%20%26quot%3Bwrong%20statements%20about%20Shahaji%20Chhatrapati%20Maharaj%2C%20Rajmata%20Jijau%20Chhatrapati%20Shivaji%20Maharaj%20and%20Chhatrapati%20Sambhaji%20Maharaj%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%2C%20in%20what%20was%20seen%20as%20a%20dig%20at%20Samajwadi%20Party%20MLA%20Abu%20Azmi%2C%20who%20had%20recently%20praised%20Aurangzeb.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20March%204%2C%20BJP%20leader%20Navneet%20Rana%20also%20demanded%20the%20demolition%20of%20Aurangzeb's%20grave.%20%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20request%20Maharashtra%20government%20that%20the%20way%20Aurangabad's%20name%20was%20changed%20and%20kept%20after%20our%20God%20Sambhaji%20Maharaj%2C%20Aurangzeb's%20grave%20should%20also%20be%20demolished%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20former%20BJP%20MP%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EControversy%20Over%20Abu%20Azmi's%20Remarks%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20Abu%20Azmi%20was%20suspended%20from%20the%20Maharashtra%20legislative%20assembly%20till%20the%20end%20of%20the%20budget%20session%20over%20his%20remarks%20praising%20Aurangzeb.%20Calling%20the%20Mughal%20emperor%20a%20great%20administrator%2C%20Mr%20Azmi%20had%20said%20he%20was%20depicted%20wrongly%20in%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAurangzeb%20built%20many%20temples.%20I%20do%20not%20consider%20Aurangzeb%20a%20cruel%20administrator.%20Also%2C%20the%20battle%20between%20Chhatrapati%20Sambhaji%20Maharaj%20and%20Aurangzeb%20was%20a%20battle%20for%20state%20administration.%20That%20battle%20was%20not%20about%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims%20anywhere%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20during%20Aurangzeb's%20time%2C%20India's%20border%20extended%20to%20Afghanistan.%20%26quot%3BAt%20that%20time%2C%20our%20GDP%20was%2024%20per%20cent...%20India%20was%20called%20Sone%20Ki%20Chidiya%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20his%20remarks%2C%20coming%20amid%20strong%20emotions%20stirred%20by%20the%20Vicky%20Kaushal-starrer%20'Chhaava'%20that%20depicted%20the%20torture%20of%20Sambhaji%20Maharaj%2C%20had%20drawn%20massive%20criticism.%20Police%20cases%20were%20filed%20against%20him%20and%20despite%20his%20later%20withdrawal%20of%20the%20comment%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20Fadnavis%20had%20said%20he%20would%20be%20%26quot%3B100%20per%20cent%20put%20in%20jail%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Tomb%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAurangzeb%2C%20who%20died%20in%201707%20at%20the%20age%20of%2087%2C%20is%20buried%20in%20Khuldabad%2C%2025%20kilometers%20from%20Aurangabad%2C%20where%20his%20wife's%20tomb%2C%20'Bibi%20ka%20maqbara%26quot%3B%20is%20located.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20will%2C%20Aurangzeb%20had%20expressed%20the%20wish%20that%20he%20be%20buried%20in%20Khuldabad%2C%20where%20his%20guru%2C%20Sufi%20saint%20Syed%20Zainuddin%2C%20is%20buried.%20The%20tomb%20lies%20within%20the%20complex%20of%20Syed%20Zainuddin.%20He%20also%20left%20instructions%20that%20he%20be%20buried%20in%20a%20simple%2C%20open-air%20tomb.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20the%20Nizam%20of%20Hyderabad%20installed%20a%20marble%20grill%20around%20the%20tomb%20at%20the%20request%20of%20Lord%20Curzon%2C%20the%20then%20Viceroy%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741628340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fkc4vfof8_aurangzeb_625x300_10_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%