Mizoram%20following%20the%202021%20military%20coup%20and%20provide%20humanitarian%20assistance.%20However%2C%20many%20of%20them%20are%20unwilling%20to%20return%2C%20even%20though%20their%20villages%20are%20visible%20just%20across%20the%20border%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20chief%20minister%20said%20in%20the%20assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20believe%20many%20people%20think%20that%20unrestricted%20movement%20between%20India%20and%20Myanmar%20is%20not%20a%20good%20idea%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhile%20we%20value%20freedom%20of%20movement%2C%20the%20central%20government's%20decision%20on%20this%20matter%20is%20necessary%2C%20and%20might%20lead%20to%20positive%20outcomes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2021-03%2F7rjm6fjo_indian-flag-at-indiamyanmar-borderreuters-_625x300_25_March_21.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMizoram%20has%20given%20shelter%20to%20over%2040%2C000%20refugees%20from%20Myanmar%2C%20where%20the%20junta%20and%20pro-democracy%20ethnic%20rebels%20are%20at%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20FMR%2C%20though%20it%20was%20not%20called%20by%20that%20name%20formally%2C%20began%20in%20the%201950s%20when%20Indian%20and%20Myanmar%20citizens%20were%20allowed%20to%20enter%20either%20side%20without%20passport%20or%20visa%20up%20to%2040%20km.%20While%20Myanmar%20citizens%20could%20stay%20for%2072%20hours%20in%20India%2C%20Indians%20could%20stay%20for%20only%2024%20hours%20in%20Myanmar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201968%2C%20India%20tightened%20the%20FMR%20with%20a%20new%20permit%20system%2C%20to%20be%20issued%20by%20either%20side%20for%20their%20citizens%20for%20temporary%20entry.%20The%20rise%20of%20insurgency%20in%20Manipur%2C%20Mizoram%2C%20and%20Nagaland%20then%20had%20sparked%20concerns%20over%20the%20FMR%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202004%2C%20India%20limited%20the%20FMR%20distance%20to%2016%20km%20from%2040%20km.%20In%20addition%2C%20instead%20of%20allowing%20people%20to%20cross%20from%20multiple%20points%2C%20only%20three%20places%20were%20allowed%20to%20be%20used%20as%20the%20gateways%20-%20Pangsau%20in%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%2C%20Moreh%20in%20Manipur%2C%20and%20Zokhawthar%20in%20Mizoram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20India%20and%20Myanmar%20signed%20the%20Agreement%20on%20Land%20Border%20Crossing%2C%20which%20formalised%20the%20FMR.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffree-movement-limit-on-indo-myanmar-border-tightened-to-10-km-with-pass-7337819%5C%22%3Erules%20were%20last%20updated%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20December%202024%20amid%20the%20Meitei-Kuki%20ethnic%20tensions%20in%20Manipur.%20The%20new%20rules%20further%20restricted%20movements%20of%20people%20from%2016%20km%20under%20the%20FMR%20to%2010%20km%2C%20on%20either%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20biometric%20details%20of%20Myanmar%20nationals%20crossing%20over%20to%20India%20using%20border%20passes%20are%20captured%20by%20Assam%20Rifles'%20representatives%20during%20entry%20and%20exit%2C%20the%20new%20rules%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741621740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Fve8spv6_lalduhoma-_625x300_21_February_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmizoram-chief-minister-lalduhoma-flags-free-movement-regime-fmr-side-effects-7893628%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mizoram%20Chief%20Minister%20Lalduhoma%20on%20Monday%20expressed%20concerns%20over%20a%20rise%20in%20smuggling%20activity%20in%20the%20state%2C%20and%20pointed%20at%20the%20free%20movement%20regime%20(FMR)%20between%20India%20and%20Myanmar%20as%20one%20of%20the%20factors%20responsible%20for%20it.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmizoram-chief-minister-lalduhoma-flags-free-movement-regime-fmr-side-effects-7893628%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Six%20Indians%20Make%20It%20To%20ICC%20Team%20Of%20Champions%20Trophy%202025.%20Rohit%20Ignored%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20talismanic%20Virat%20Kohli%20was%20the%20biggest%20name%20among%20six%20Indian%20players%20picked%20in%20the%2012-member%20'Team%20of%20the%20Tournament'%20picked%20by%20the%20International%20Cricket%20Council%20for%20the%20Champions%20Trophy.%20India%20beat%20New%20Zealand%20by%20four%20wickets%20in%20the%20final%20in%20Dubai%20on%20Sunday%20to%20win%20the%20tournament%20for%20the%20third%20time%20after%202002%20(joint%20winners)%20and%202013.%20India%20have%20been%20runners-up%20twice%20in%202000%20and%202017.%20Besides%20Kohli%2C%20Shreyas%20Iyer%2C%20wicketkeeper-batter%20KL%20Rahul%2C%20mystery%20spinner%20Varun%20Chakravarthy%20and%20pacer%20Mohammed%20Shami%20featured%20in%20the%20playing%20XI%2C%20while%20all-rounder%20Axar%20Patel%20was%20named%20the%2012th%20man.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Black%20Caps%20have%20four%20members%20of%20their%20squad%20making%20the%20team%2C%20including%20Player%20of%20the%20Tournament%20Rachin%20Ravindra%2C%20with%20Mitchell%20Santner%20being%20named%20captain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20players%20from%20Afghanistan%20also%20made%20the%20cut%20after%20the%20Asian%20nation%20won%20their%20first-ever%20ICC%20Men's%20Champions%20Trophy%20match%20in%20their%20debut%20appearance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20top%20of%20the%20order%2C%20Ravindra%20was%20an%20expected%20selection%20after%20he%20scored%20two%20centuries%20and%20topped%20the%20run-scoring%20charts%20with%20263.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20knock%20of%20112%20against%20Bangladesh%20was%20instrumental%20in%20seeing%20New%20Zealand%20over%20the%20line%20and%20his%20108%20in%20the%20semi-final%20against%20South%20Africa%20showed%20he%20is%20dangerous%20wherever%20he%20bats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERavindra%20was%20joined%20by%20Ibrahim%20Zadran%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20order.%20The%2023-year-old%20Afghan%20more%20than%20left%20his%20mark%20on%20the%20tournament%2C%20playing%20a%20brilliant%20knock%20of%20177%20--%20the%20highest-ever%20Champions%20Trophy%20score%20--%20against%20England%20in%20the%20group%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20Kohli%20slots%20in%20at%20number%20three%20after%20he%20finished%20fifth%20in%20the%20run-scoring%20charts%20with%20218%20at%20an%20average%20of%2054.50.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKohli%20made%20a%20memorable%20unbeaten%20century%20in%20his%20side's%20group-stage%20win%20over%20Pakistan%20and%20a%20crucial%2084%20in%20the%20semi-final%20win%20over%20world%20champions%20Australia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETeammates%20Shreyas%20and%20Rahul%20join%20him%20in%20the%20middle-order%20after%20impressive%20tournaments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIyer%20was%20India's%20top%20run-scorer%20in%20the%20tournament%2C%20with%20two%20half-centuries%20helping%20him%20to%20243%20runs%20in%20total%2C%20while%20Rahul%20finished%20with%20an%20average%20of%20140%20thanks%20to%20unbeaten%20knocks%20of%2042%20and%2034%20in%20the%20semi-final%20and%20final%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENew%20Zealand's%20Glenn%20Phillips%20is%20selected%20at%20number%20six%20after%20a%20brilliant%20performance%20with%20the%20bat%20and%20in%20the%20field.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPhillips'%20diving%20one-handed%20catch%20to%20dismiss%20Shubman%20Gill%20in%20the%20final%20was%20one%20of%20three%20iconic%20takes%20across%20the%20tournament%2C%20while%20the%2028-year-old%20scored%20one%20half%20century%20against%20Pakistan%20and%20took%20two%20wickets%20against%20South%20Africa%20in%20the%20semi-final%20to%20go%20alongside%20an%20unbeaten%2049.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAzmatullah%20Omarzai%20is%20the%20second%20Afghan%20named%20in%20the%20team.%20The%20fast-bowling%20all-rounder%20had%20a%20fantastic%20tournament%20with%20both%20bat%20and%20ball%2C%20finishing%20with%20seven%20wickets%20at%2020%20and%20126%20runs