2C%22summary%22%3A%22FM%20Sitharaman%20-%20in%20Union%20Budget%20speech%20-%20unveiled%20a%20slew%20of%20measures%20to%20open%20Indian%20maritime%20economy%2C%20including%20%E2%82%B925%2C000-crore%20maritime%20development%20fund%2C%20tax%20breaks%2C%20and%20new%20shipbuilding%20subsidy%20policy%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kerala%20Woman%20Skips%20Food%2C%20Relies%20On%20Water%20For%206%20Months%20To%20Lose%20Weight%2C%20Dies%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAn%2018-year-old%20girl%20from%20Thalassery%20suffering%20from%20the%20eating%20disorder%20'Anorexia'%20died%20at%20Thalassery%20co-operative%20hospital%20where%20she%20was%20undergoing%20treatment%20after%20she%20abstained%20from%20proper%20food%20for%20almost%20six%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESree%20Nanda%2C%20a%20native%20of%20Meruvambai%20Thalassery%20who%20died%20on%20Sunday%2C%20used%20to%20follow%20online%20portals%20for%20a%20weight%20loss%20diet%20and%20was%20surviving%20on%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Nagesh%20Manohar%20Prabhu%2C%20a%20consultant%20physician%20at%20Thalaserry%20Co-operative%20Hospital%2C%20said%20that%20she%20was%20brought%20to%20the%20hospital%20around%2012%20days%20ago%20and%20was%20directly%20admitted%20to%20the%20ICU.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20physician%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BShe%20was%20hardly%2024%20kgs%2C%20bedridden.%20Her%20sugar%20levels%2C%20sodium%2C%20and%20BP%20were%20low.%20She%20was%20out%20on%20ventilator%20support.%20But%20her%20condition%20did%20not%20improve%2C%20and%20she%20succumbed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20doctors%2C%20anorexia%20is%20an%20eating%20disorder%20causing%20people%20to%20be%20obsessed%20about%20weight%20and%20what%20they%20eat.%20Under%20this%20condition%2C%20even%20when%20people%20are%20thin%2C%20the%20person%20affected%20thinks%20they%20are%20overweight%20and%20will%20not%20eat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20family%20and%20doctors%2C%20the%20condition%20persisted%20for%20about%20five%20to%20six%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20hardly%20eating%20anything%2C%20and%20she%20hid%20it%20from%20the%20family.%20About%20five%20months%20back%2C%20she%20was%20taken%20to%20the%20hospital%2C%20and%20the%20doctors%20advised%20that%20she%20needed%20to%20eat%20and%20asked%20the%20family%20to%20get%20a%20psychiatric%20consultation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20her%20relative%2C%20she%20used%20to%20hide%20the%20food%20her%20parents%20gave%20her%2C%20and%20survived%20on%20hot%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20taken%20to%20Kozhikode%20Medical%20College%20Hospital%20two%20months%20back%2C%20and%20tests%20were%20done.%20Doctors%20advised%20the%20family%20to%20feed%20her%20and%20to%20get%20psychiatric%20consultation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20weeks%20back%2C%20her%20blood%20sugar%20dropped%2C%20and%20she%20had%20breathing%20issues%20and%20was%20immediately%20admitted%20to%20Thalaserry%20Co-operative%20Hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%2C%20many%20family%20members%2C%20acquaintances%2C%20and%20celebrities%20have%20suffered%20from%20anorexia%20nervosa%2C%20or%20AN%2C%20a%20severe%20mental%20condition%20characterised%20by%20excessive%20worries%20about%20weight%2C%20form%2C%20and%20self-esteem.%20An%20eating%20disorder%2C%20dietary%20restriction%2C%20purposeful%20vomiting%2C%20and%20acute%20emaciation%20are%20all%20symptoms%20of%20AN.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741618560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2F42g1ig6o_water-generic_625x300_10_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fanorexia-disorder-kerala-woman-skips-food-relies-on-water-for-6-months-to-lose-weight-dies-7893125%22%2C%22