on%20Shops%20Run%20By%20Hindus%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMaharashtra%20minister%20Nitesh%20Rane%20announced%20a%20new%20certification%20for%20mutton%20shops%20that%20would%20be%20run%20only%20by%20Hindus.%20Announcing%20the%20Malhar%20certification%20initiative%2C%20he%20urged%20people%20not%20to%20purchase%20mutton%20from%20%26quot%3Bplaces%20where%20Malhar%20certification%20is%20not%20available%26quot%3B.%20The%20effort%2C%20he%20added%2C%20would%20make%20the%20youth%20of%20the%20Hindu%20community%20%26quot%3Bfinancially%20empowered%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bno%20adulteration%20will%20be%20found%20in%20the%20mutton%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Malhar%20certification%20will%20be%20similar%20to%20the%20existing%20halal%20certification%20in%20India%2C%20where%20the%20animals%20are%20slaughtered%20according%20to%20the%20Islamic%20laws.%20The%20other%20process%20is%20%26quot%3Bjhatka%26quot%3B%2C%20where%20the%20neck%20of%20an%20animal%20is%20severed%20with%20a%20single%20blow%20--%20as%20opposed%20to%20the%20halal%20process%20of%20draining%20the%20blood%20first.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEach%20side%20has%20traditionally%20claimed%20that%20its%20process%20is%20more%20humane.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20Mr%20Rane%20today%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThrough%20Malhar%20Certification%2C%20we%20will%20have%20access%20to%20our%20rightful%20mutton%20shops%20and%20there%20will%20be%20a%20100%20percent%20Hindu%20community%20and%20the%20person%20selling%20will%20also%20be%20a%20Hindu%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22mr%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FQdlcTN1UL5%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FQdlcTN1UL5%3C%2Fa%3E)%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FhIbS1SG1Ia%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FhIbS1SG1Ia%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Nitesh%20Rane%20(%40NiteshNRane)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FNiteshNRane%2Fstatus%2F1898996139401109537%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%2010%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDescribing%20the%20%C2%A0launch%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bvery%20important%20step%20for%20the%20Hindu%20community%20in%20Maharashtra'%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20appeal%20to%20you%20to%20use%20Malhar%20certification%20as%20much%20as%20possible%20and%20in%20fact%2C%20not%20to%20buy%20mutton%20from%20places%20where%20Malhar%20certification%20is%20not%20available%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20right-wing%20groups%20in%20several%20BJP-ruled%20states%20have%20started%20a%20campaign%20against%20halal%20meat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20controversy%20started%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20where%20right-wing%20leaders%20called%20for%20the%20boycott%20of%20halal%20meat%2C%20labelling%20it%20an%20%26quot%3Beconomic%20jihad%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20claimed%20the%20halal%20process%20was%20discriminatory%2C%20since%20Hindus%20cannot%20be%20employed%20in%20the%20slaughter%20and%20packing%20chain.%20Besides%20domestic%20consumption%2C%20halal%20meat%20is%20also%20a%20huge%20industry%20in%20terms%20of%20exports%2C%20because%20Muslim%20nations%20insist%20on%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20while%20the%20word%20halal%20is%20used%20mostly%20in%20the%20context%20of%20meat%2C%20its%20actual%20meaning%20is%20%26quot%3Bpermissible%26quot%3B%20under%20Islamic%20law.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20vegetarian%20food%20or%20fish%20products%20or%20even%20pharma%20items%20that%20contain%20alcohol%20or%20pork%20(fat)%20or%20other%20items%20banned%20under%20Islam%2C%20are%20considered%20contaminated%20and%20not%20halal.%20This%20is%20why%20halal%20certification%20is%20also%20given%20to%20many%20such%20products%2C%20especially%20for%20exports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20right%20wing%20has%20contended%20that%20it%20is%20essential%20to%20set%20up%20an%20alternate%20system%20for%20youths%2C%20and%20there%20have%20been%20demands%20for%20a%20jhatka%20certification%20authority%20from%20some%20quarters.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741616940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2F1nrjtqu8_nitesh-rane-_625x300_10_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmalhar-certification-nitesh-rane-maharashtra-minister-launches-rightful-mutton-shops-run-by-hindus-7892610%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Maharashtra%20minister%20Nitesh%20Rane%20announced%20a%20new%20certification%20for%20mutton%20shops%20that%20would%20be%20run%20only%20by%20Hindus.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmalhar-certification-nitesh-rane-maharashtra-minister-launches-rightful-mutton-shops-run-by-hindus-7892610%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Probe%20Agency%20Team%20Attacked%20After%20Searches%20At%20Bhupesh%20Baghel's%20Home%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EEnforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20officials%2C%20who%20had%20searched%20former%20Chhattisgarh%20chief%20minister%20Bhupesh%20Baghel's%20premises%20in%20a%20money%20laundering%20investigation%20against%20his%20son%20in%20the%20alleged%20liquor%20scam%20case%2C%20were%20attacked%20by%20a%20group%20of%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficials%20alleged%20the%20attackers%20were%20Congress%20workers%2C%20who%20were%20upset%20over%20the%20searches%20at%20Mr%20Baghel's%20premises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20car%20of%20a%20deputy%20director-level%20ED%20officer%20was%20also%20attacked%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVisuals%20of%20the%20attack%20show%20a%20large%20group%20of%20people%20surrounding%20the%20ED%20officers%20and%20hitting%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20premises%20of%20Mr%20Baghel's%20son%20Chaitanya%20Baghel%20in%20Bhilai%2C%20aide%20Laxmi%20Narayan%20Bansal%20alias%20Pappu%20Bansal%2C%20and%20some%20others%20were%20searched%20under%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%20(PMLA)%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChaitanya%20Baghel%20shares%20the%20Bhilai%20accommodation%20with%20his%20father%20and%20so%20the%20premises%20were%20being%20covered.%20Chaitanya%20Baghel%20is%20suspected%20to%20be%20the%20%26quot%3Brecipient%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20proceeds%20of%20crime%20of%20the%20liquor%20scam%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbout%2014-15%20premises%20were%20searched%20in%20the%20state%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741616160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fa7dkfrng_ed-raid_625x300_10_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fprobe-agency-ed-team-attacked-allegedly-by-congress-workers-after-searches-on-bhupesh-baghels-chhattisgarh-home-7892918%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20officials%2C%20who%20had%20searched%20former%20Chhattisgarh%20chief%20minister%20Bhupesh%20Baghel's%20premises%20in%20a%20money%20laundering%20investigation%20against%20his%20son%20in%20the%20alleged%20liquor%20scam%20case%2C%20were%20attacked%20by%20a%20group%20of%20people.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fprobe-agency-ed-team-attacked-allegedly-by-congress-workers-after-searches-on-bhupesh-baghels-chhattisgarh-home-7892918%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rohit%20Clears%20Air%20On%20Playing%202027%20World%20Cup%2C%20Says%3A%20%26quot%3BIt%20Wouldn't%20Be...%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rohit%20Sharma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F857-rohit-sharma-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERohit%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E%20gave%20a%20big%20statement%20after%20India's%20Champions%20Trophy%202025%20triumph%20clearing%20the%20air%20on%20his%20future%20in%20ODIs.%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20not%20going%20to%20retire%20from%20this%20format.%20Just%20to%20make%20sure%20no%20rumours%20are%20spread%20moving%20forward.%20Koi%20future%20plan%20hai%20nahi%2C%20jo%20chal%20raha%20hai%20chalega%20(there%20is%20no%20future%20plan%2C%20whatever%20is%20going%20on%20will%20continue%20as%20it%20is)%2C%26quot%3B%20Rohit%20Sharma%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20hunger%20even%20in%20guys%20who%20have%20played%20a%20lot%20of%20cricket%20and%20it%20rubs%20down%20on%20even%20the%20younger%20players.%20We%20have%20five%20to%20six%20players%20who%20are%20real%20stalwarts.%20It%20makes%20the%20job%20easier%20for%20all%20of%20us.%26quot%3B%20That%20statement%20assured%20all%20that%20he%20is%20not%20going%20anywhere%20soon.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20India%20captain%20Rohit%20Sharma%20will%20be%2038%20in%20two%20months'%20time%20and%20with%20India's%20next%20major%20ODI%20tournament%20being%20the%202027%20ODI%20World%20Cup%2C%20it%20remains%20to%20be%20seen%20how%20long%20he%20plays%20at%20the%20top%20level%20in%20the%20ODI%20format.%20A%20day%20after%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%202025%20triumph%2C%20he%20revealed%20that%20he%20is%20not%20yet%20thinking%20about%20the%202027%20World%20Cup.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRight%20now%2C%20I%20am%20taking%20things%20as%20they%20come.%20It%20wouldn't%20be%20fair%20for%20me%20to%20think%20too%20far%20ahead.%20At%20this%20moment%2C%20my%20focus%20is%20on%20playing%20well%20and%20maintaining%20the%20right%20mindset.%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20draw%20any%20lines%20and%20say%20whether%20I%20will%20or%20won't%20play%20in%20the%202027%20World%20Cup%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20on%20Jio%20Hotstar.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20no%20point%20in%20making%20such%20statements%20right%20now.%20Realistically%2C%20I%20have%20always%20taken%20my%20career%20one%20step%20at%20a%20time.%20I%20don't%20like%20thinking%20too%20far%20into%20the%20future%2C%20and%20I%20haven't%20done%20so%20in%20the%20past%20either.%20For%20now%2C%20I%20am%20enjoying%20my%20cricket%20and%20the%20time%20I%20spend%20with%20this%20team.%20I%20hope%20my%20teammates%20enjoy%20my%20presence%20as%20well.%20That's%20all%20that%20matters%20at%20this%20point.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20leading%20India%20to%20an%20unbeaten%20ICC%20Men's%20Champions%20Trophy%20victory%2C%20captain%20Rohit%20Sharma%20opened%20up%20about%20the%20team's%20journey%2C%20overcoming%20challenges%2C%20and%20his%20personal%20outlook%20on%20the%20future.%20Rohit%20shared%20insights%20into%20India's%20approach%2C%20their%20ability%20to%20handle%20adversity%2C%20and%20the%20evolution%20of%20their%20mindset%20since%20past%20tournament%20heartbreaks.%20India's%20Champions%20Trophy%20campaign%20was%20nothing%20short%20of%20remarkable.%20In%20the%20final%2C%20they%20defeated%20New%20Zealand%20by%20four%20wickets%20at%20the%20Dubai%20International%20Stadium.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20went%20undefeated%20despite%20losing%20all%20five%20tosses.%20Yet%2C%20we%20still%20won%20the%20trophy%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CWinning%20a%20tournament%20without%20a%20single%20defeat%20is%20a%20massive%20achievement%20in%20itself%2C%20and%20it%20gives%20me%20immense%20satisfaction.%20Until%20we%20lifted%20the%20trophy%2C%20no%20one%20really%20thought%20about%20it.%20But%20after%20the%20victory%2C%20it%20hit%20us%E2%80%94we%20had%20gone%20through%20the%20entire%20tournament%20unbeaten.%20That%20realization%20made%20it%20even%20more%20special%2C%26quot%3B%20Rohit%20said%20on%20JioHotstar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERohit%20credited%20the%20team's%20unity%20and%20clarity%20of%20roles%20for%20their%20success.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20an%20incredibly%20solid%20team%2C%20and%20it's%20a%20joy%20to%20play%20alongside%20such%20committed%20individuals.%20Everyone%20knows%20their%20role%20and%20responsibilities%E2%80%94what%20needs%20to%20be%20done%20and%20what%20must%20be%20avoided.%20Of%20course%2C%20emotions%20run%20high%20on%20the%20field.%20Sometimes%2C%20I%20get%20a%20bit%20carried%20away%2C%20but%20it's%20all%20in%20the%20spirit%20of%20the%20game.%20The%20main%20goal%20is%20to%20win%2C%20and%20we%20are%20ready%20to%20do%20whatever%20it%20takes%20to%20achieve%20that.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPreparation%20played%20a%20key%20role%20in%20ensuring%20India%20could%20adapt%20to%20conditions%20without%20Bumrah%2C%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20the%20Australia%20tour%2C%20we%20had%20about%2020-25%20days%20before%20the%20tournament.%20We%20closely%20monitored%20the%20ILT20%20matches%20to%20study%20the%20pitches%20and%20playing%20conditions.%20We%20analyzed%20what%20kind%20of%20bowlers%20were%20needed%20for%20those%20surfaces%20and%20shaped%20our%20squad%20accordingly.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReflecting%20on%20India's%20previous%20failures%20in%20ICC%20tournaments%2C%20Rohit%20pointed%20to%20a%20significant%20change%20in%20mindset%20that%20helped%20them%20finally%20cross%20the%20finish%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20always%20unfortunate%20that%20we%20came%20so%20close%20to%20winning%20major%20tournaments%20but%20couldn't%20get%20over%20the%20line.%20In%20the%202015%20World%20Cup%20semi-final%20against%20Australia%2C%20we%20made%20mistakes%20we%20hadn't%20made%20in%20the%20previous%20matches.%20The%20same%20thing%20happened%20in%202016%2C%202017%2C%20and%20even%20the%202023%20World%20Cup%20final%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20admitted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20turning%20point%20came%20when%20the%20team%20decided%20to%20prioritise%20collective%20success%20over%20individual%20milestones.%20%E2%80%9CBefore%20the%202023%20World%20Cup%2C%20we%20had%20serious%20discussions%20about%20shifting%20our%20mindset.%20The%20focus%20was%20no%20longer%20on%20individual%20milestones%E2%80%94scoring%20a%20hundred%20or%20taking%20five%20wickets%E2%80%94because%2C%20in%20the%20end%2C%20if%20the%20team%20doesn't%20win%2C%20those%20achievements%20don't%20matter.%20I%20learned%20this%20the%20hard%20way%20in%202019.%20I%20scored%20five%20centuries%2C%20but%20what%20did%20it%20mean%20when%20we%20didn't%20win%20the%20trophy%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERohit%20also%20addressed%20how%20he%20wanted%20other%20teams%20to%20perceive%20India%20moving%20forward.%20%E2%80%9CI%20don't%20want%20to%20dictate%20how%20other%20teams%20should%20see%20us.%20The%20only%20thing%20I%20want%20is%20for%20them%20never%20to%20take%20us%20lightly.%20Even%20if%20we%20are%20five%20wickets%20down%2C%20we%20have%20the%20ability%20to%20fight%20back%20and%20turn%20the%20game%20around.%20Until%20the%20last%20ball%20of%20the%20match%20is%20bowled%2C%20our%20opponents%20should%20always%20feel%20the%20pressure%20of%20playing%20against%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20IANS%20inputs%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741614660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fcq1oc96o_rohit-sharma_625x300_10_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-champions-trophy-2025%2Fwhether-i-will-or-wont-play-2027-world-cup-rohit-sharmas-big-statement-day-after-ruling-out-retirement-7892578%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20captain%20Rohit%20Sharma%20will%20be%2038%20in%20two%20months'%20time%20and%20with%20India's%20next%20major%20ODI%20tournament%20being%20the%202027%20ODI%20World%20Cup%2C%20it%20remains%20to%20be%20seen%20how%20long%20he%20plays%20at%20the%20top%20level%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-champions-trophy-2025%2Fwhether-i-will-or-wont-play-2027-world-cup-rohit-sharmas-big-statement-day-after-ruling-out-retirement-7892578%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UK%20National%20Arrested%20In%20Andamans%20For%20%26quot%3BSexually%20Assaulting%26quot%3B%20Indian%20Woman%3A%20Cops%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAndaman%20and%20Nicobar%20Islands%20police%20has%20arrested%20a%20UK%20national%20for%20allegedly%20sexually%20assaulting%20a%20woman%