dia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FCK_6-1_11zon-1741342824-768x512.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FCK_6-1_11zon-1741342824-1536x1024.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FCK_6-1_11zon-1741342824-2048x1365.jpg%202048w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FCK_6-1_11zon-1741342824-1200x800.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FCK_6-1_11zon-1741342824-150x100.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-412101%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221756%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ECybageKhushboo%20helps%20its%20students%20improve%20their%20communication%20skills%20so%20they%20can%20be%20more%20confident%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20ahead%2C%20CybageKhushboo%20has%20ambitious%20expansion%20plans.%20With%20an%20ambitious%20goal%20of%20awarding%20Rs%2035%20crore%20in%20scholarships%20over%20the%20next%20five%20years%2C%20CybageKhushboo%20is%20set%20to%20create%20an%20even%20greater%20impact.%20In%202024-25%20alone%2C%20the%20initiative%20granted%20over%20Rs%206.66%20crore%20in%20scholarships%2C%20empowering%20500%20new%20students%20and%20renewing%20support%20for%20more%20than%20700%20others%2C%20ensuring%20they%20continue%20their%20education%20without%20financial%20barriers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20currently%20being%20run%20in%20three%20locations%3A%20Pune%2C%20where%20the%20headquarters%20are%20based%2C%20and%20Gandhinagar%20and%20Hyderabad.%20%E2%80%9CAt%20the%20moment%2C%20we%20are%20restricted%20to%20these%20three%20places%20because%20that%E2%80%99s%20where%20our%20office%20is%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ritu%20explains.%20The%20team%20plans%20to%20expand%20to%20other%20states%2C%20though%20the%20challenge%20lies%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20offices%20in%20those%20regions.%20As%20a%20solution%2C%20they%20collaborate%20with%20NGOs%20that%20operate%20in%20similar%20spaces%20to%20help%20with%20the%20expansion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EOpening%20doors%20to%20education%3A%20A%20simple%20and%20inclusive%20application%20process%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20application%20process%20for%20students%20is%20conducted%20in%20two%20ways.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20method%20is%20through%20the%20programme%E2%80%99s%20website%2C%20which%20goes%20live%20in%20July%202025.%20This%20timing%20is%20in%20line%20with%20the%20results%20of%20various%20exams%2C%20which%20are%20typically%20declared%20in%20May%20and%20June.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20students%20who%20do%20not%20have%20access%20to%20a%20computer%20or%20any%20device%2C%20Cybage%20has%20set%20up%20a%20support%20system.%20%E2%80%9CAny%20student%20who%20does%20not%20have%20access%20to%20a%20computer%20or%20any%20device%20can%20come%20to%20Cybage%20at%20our%20office.%20We%20set%20up%20a%20kiosk%20at%20the%20entrance%20for%20these%20students%2C%20and%20one%20of%20our%20CSR%20volunteers%20helps%20them%20fill%20out%20the%20form%20and%20submit%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20method%20is%20through%20direct%20collaborations%20with%20colleges.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20direct%20tie-ups%20with%20colleges%2C%20where%20we%20inform%20them%20about%20CybageKhushboo.%20Every%20year%2C%20they%20receive%20applications%20and%20send%20us%20the%20ones%20they%20feel%20fit%20the%20criteria%20for%20the%20scholarships%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ritu.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20CybageKhushboo%20has%20formed%20partnerships%20with%2019%20colleges%2C%20and%20the%20team%20continues%20to%20add%20more%20institutions%20each%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Ritu%20puts%20it%2C%20%E2%80%9CEducation%20is%20not%20just%20about%20textbooks.%20It%E2%80%99s%20about%20building%20character%2C%20confidence%2C%20and%20the%20ability%20to%20contribute%20to%20the%20world.%20Through%20CybageKhushboo%2C%20we%20are%20trying%20to%20achieve%20that.%